sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant ProjectsUI as Projects Dashboard + ProjectForm
    participant ProjectAPI as /api/projects endpoints
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    Admin->>ProjectsUI: Open /dashboard/projects
    ProjectsUI->>ProjectAPI: GET /api/projects?page=1
    ProjectAPI->>DB: Query LAB_PROJECT records
    DB-->>ProjectAPI: Project list
    ProjectAPI-->>ProjectsUI: List payload
    ProjectsUI-->>Admin: Render project list

    Admin->>ProjectsUI: Create or update project
    ProjectsUI->>ProjectAPI: POST or PATCH /api/projects
    ProjectAPI->>DB: Persist project, tags, and links
    DB-->>ProjectAPI: Persisted project
    ProjectAPI-->>ProjectsUI: Success response

    Admin->>ProjectsUI: Delete project
    ProjectsUI->>ProjectAPI: DELETE /api/projects/:id
    ProjectAPI->>DB: Delete project
    DB-->>ProjectAPI: Delete result
    ProjectAPI-->>ProjectsUI: Success
